            , Constable, depos'd, That he took the Prisoner at the White Horse in Friday-Street, and searching, found 3 of the Rings upon her, and another they found next Day, which she had pawn'd in the Compter, which Rings being produc'd in Court the Prosecutor swore they were his. 
               <persName id="t17271017-6-person60">
                  Mark 
                  Savill 
               <interp inst="t17271017-6-person60" type="surname" value="Savill"></interp>
