             depos'd, That he was present at her Examination, when she confess'd she opend she Locks with a Knife, and took the Money and Rings, with which she had liv'd very extravagantly; adding, that the Waggoner she came up with never had such a Passenger in his Life. 
               <persName id="t17271017-6-person61">
                  Richard 
